      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable mechanical order, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by both performance and reliability. The exterior retains its original luster, complemented by a well-preserved interior that reflects a history of attentive ownership. We invite you to evaluate the superior caliber of this professional-grade automotive offering.",
