    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! Whether you're commuting to work or planning a fun weekend getaway, this car is ready for it all. It's been a great companion to me, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it too. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
