      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential for a purely analog driving experience. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos system service and a structural subframe inspection, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under load. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and communicative feedback these M-cars are known for. While displaying minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, its performance remains uncompromised and the power delivery is exceptionally linear.",
      "price": 34500.0,
