    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, though the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows light natural creasing from entry and exit. All technological features, from the responsive touchscreen infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, operate exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a consistent service history that highlights regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This car is ideal for someone seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
      "price": 33500.0,
